1
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:54,540
=Coming to Court Soon=

2
00:00:56,300 --> 00:00:58,300
=Episode 6=

3
00:01:06,740 --> 00:01:08,270
You two really don't know each other?

4
00:01:12,190 --> 00:01:12,830
Brother.

5
00:01:12,830 --> 00:01:13,270
(Personal File Form)

6
00:01:13,270 --> 00:01:15,550
That day, you took on
a dozen punks by yourself.

7
00:01:15,910 --> 00:01:16,470
I was there.

8
00:01:19,860 --> 00:01:20,860
That was so cool.

9
00:01:24,780 --> 00:01:25,470
Tell me.

10
00:01:26,070 --> 00:01:27,110
Why were you drunk driving?

11
00:01:27,910 --> 00:01:29,340
Why did you hit the police officers?

12
00:01:32,500 --> 00:01:33,750
It's all because of Li Hai.

13
00:01:34,420 --> 00:01:35,220
How is it?

14
00:01:35,860 --> 00:01:36,750
Do I look even better

15
00:01:36,750 --> 00:01:37,780
in this outfit?

16
00:01:39,780 --> 00:01:41,340
It's chilly outside at night.

17
00:01:41,340 --> 00:01:43,310
Don't take off your coat.

18
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:46,030
This family is lucky to have you.

19
00:01:48,060 --> 00:01:49,700
Now you realize it?

20
00:01:53,750 --> 00:01:54,580
Wretched woman.

21
00:01:54,980 --> 00:01:55,950
Shameless!

22
00:01:56,190 --> 00:01:56,980
Li Songyan!

23
00:01:57,450 --> 00:01:58,900
Are you itching for a beating again?

24
00:01:58,910 --> 00:02:00,310
You little brat, listen up.

25
00:02:00,750 --> 00:02:01,750
She's your elder.

26
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:02,480
She's your mother!

27
00:02:02,580 --> 00:02:03,750
She isn't my mother!

28
00:02:04,100 --> 00:02:05,580
She's only a few years older than me,

29
00:02:05,580 --> 00:02:06,900
and you want me to call her mom?

30
00:02:07,060 --> 00:02:07,830
Shameless!

31
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:09,910
What nonsense are you spouting?

32
00:02:11,220 --> 00:02:12,500
He forgot my mom's anniversary.

33
00:02:26,070 --> 00:02:26,740
Songyan.

34
00:02:26,740 --> 00:02:30,020
No matter what, speaking to your father
like that is wrong.

35
00:02:30,020 --> 00:02:33,180
You should learn
to control your emotions.

36
00:02:33,180 --> 00:02:35,460
Learn to communicate with your father.

37
00:02:35,460 --> 00:02:37,630
But he's so stubborn and rigid.

38
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:38,540
How am I supposed to...

39
00:02:38,550 --> 00:02:40,280
You're thinking of giving up
before even trying?

40
00:02:40,290 --> 00:02:40,800
But Li Hai...

41
00:02:41,550 --> 00:02:43,310
If you choose to give up, I understand.

42
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:45,170
After all, your father is
an outstanding man.

43
00:02:45,180 --> 00:02:46,510
He's a well-known entrepreneur,

44
00:02:46,510 --> 00:02:47,350
and a philanthropist.

45
00:02:47,740 --> 00:02:48,950
He built Tonghai Logistics

46
00:02:49,460 --> 00:02:51,460
from the ground up.

47
00:02:52,020 --> 00:02:52,950
Who's giving up?

48
00:02:54,110 --> 00:02:54,900
But...

49
00:02:55,230 --> 00:02:56,740
Can I really do it?

50
00:02:58,950 --> 00:02:59,860
I get it now.

51
00:03:00,790 --> 00:03:02,790
What I need to do isn't
to prove that he's wrong,

52
00:03:03,110 --> 00:03:04,390
but to prove that I'm right.

53
00:03:06,630 --> 00:03:07,180
Alright.

54
00:03:07,510 --> 00:03:08,950
That's all for today.

55
00:03:09,270 --> 00:03:10,950
For now, don't leave the city.

56
00:03:11,070 --> 00:03:12,790
Be ready for our summons at any time.

57
00:03:19,110 --> 00:03:19,740
Brother.

58
00:03:20,580 --> 00:03:21,630
Can I come to you

59
00:03:21,630 --> 00:03:22,980
if I ever need help?

60
00:03:27,660 --> 00:03:35,220
(Xue Biao, auto repair shop owner)

61
00:03:37,790 --> 00:03:38,580
(Sir Xue.)

62
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,310
(Haven't seen you for a few days.)

63
00:03:40,390 --> 00:03:41,630
(Wanna play a few rounds?)

64
00:03:59,860 --> 00:04:05,420
(Deng Xing)

65
00:04:11,180 --> 00:04:12,540
(Zhou Qi)

66
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:13,490
(Zhou Qi's friend)
Zhou Qi.

67
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:14,510
(Deng Xing)
I'm so happy

68
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:15,830
you called me.

69
00:04:16,230 --> 00:04:17,020
Deng Xing.

70
00:04:19,140 --> 00:04:20,350
Can you lend me 100 thousand?

71
00:04:20,510 --> 00:04:21,900
A hundred thousand?

72
00:04:22,550 --> 00:04:23,860
Why do you need so much money?

73
00:04:24,270 --> 00:04:25,950
Are you in trouble?

74
00:04:27,530 --> 00:04:28,900
I just borrowed from a loan shark.

75
00:04:28,990 --> 00:04:29,700
It's okay.

76
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:31,340
If you don't have it, forget it.

77
00:04:31,870 --> 00:04:32,390
Bye.

78
00:04:32,660 --> 00:04:33,340
Wait.

79
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:35,580
A hundred thousand isn't a small amount.

80
00:04:36,310 --> 00:04:37,540
Give me a few days.

81
00:04:37,890 --> 00:04:38,950
I'll figure something out.

82
00:04:44,310 --> 00:04:45,310
A hundred thousand.

83
00:04:53,340 --> 00:04:58,500
(Loan Agreement)

84
00:05:09,780 --> 00:05:11,870
This is still way short.

85
00:05:22,020 --> 00:05:22,580
Hello?

86
00:05:23,660 --> 00:05:24,460
Huang Xian.

87
00:05:25,220 --> 00:05:29,540
(Black Mamba Billiards Club)

88
00:05:30,820 --> 00:05:33,100
