89
00:05:34,700 --> 00:05:35,540
Sorry.

90
00:05:35,750 --> 00:05:37,270
Four concealed triplets. I won again.

91
00:05:38,950 --> 00:05:39,830
What's going on?

92
00:05:39,990 --> 00:05:40,660
Kid.

93
00:05:40,660 --> 00:05:42,750
You're not cheating, are you?

94
00:05:45,140 --> 00:05:45,870
Kid.

95
00:05:46,020 --> 00:05:47,890
(Ma Haoda's subordinate)
Cheating in my house?

96
00:05:48,010 --> 00:05:49,300
(Huang Xian)
Do you want to die?

97
00:05:49,460 --> 00:05:50,510
I wasn't cheating.

98
00:05:51,020 --> 00:05:52,070
Our boss wants to see you.

99
00:05:53,660 --> 00:05:58,340
♪I shouldn't have let you suffer,
continuing this act♪

100
00:05:59,300 --> 00:06:03,380
♪You don't really understand me♪

101
00:06:05,060 --> 00:06:08,580
♪Why should I be the one to forgive?♪

102
00:06:08,580 --> 00:06:10,070
Brother Haoda, he's here.

103
00:06:10,380 --> 00:06:13,020
♪If we say goodbye, don't come back♪

104
00:06:13,300 --> 00:06:16,020
♪If we say goodbye, don't look pitiful♪

105
00:06:22,660 --> 00:06:23,580
I wasn't cheating.

106
00:06:25,310 --> 00:06:26,310
Just joking.

107
00:06:26,630 --> 00:06:27,270
Kid.

108
00:06:27,460 --> 00:06:28,310
Relax.

109
00:06:29,220 --> 00:06:30,270
What do you want?

110
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:31,630
I can tell.

111
00:06:32,210 --> 00:06:33,630
You're different from those people.

112
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:35,340
You came here

113
00:06:35,950 --> 00:06:37,140
