114
00:06:38,990 --> 00:06:40,190
Relax.

115
00:06:41,140 --> 00:06:43,870
I'll find you a way to make money.

116
00:06:44,390 --> 00:06:45,630
Play a round for me.

117
00:06:45,830 --> 00:06:46,750
If you win,

118
00:06:47,310 --> 00:06:48,430
we split 40-60.

119
00:06:49,190 --> 00:06:50,270
What if I lose?

120
00:06:51,900 --> 00:06:52,950
Kid.

121
00:06:53,630 --> 00:06:54,990
Have some confidence.

122
00:06:56,220 --> 00:06:57,100
I believe in you.

123
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:14,900
Brother.

124
00:07:15,190 --> 00:07:16,510
Finally off work?

125
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:17,390
You're looking for me?

126
00:07:17,990 --> 00:07:19,140
I like talking to you.

127
00:07:19,330 --> 00:07:20,190
Let's chat for a bit.

128
00:07:24,390 --> 00:07:24,900
What,

129
00:07:25,390 --> 00:07:26,340
