130
00:07:27,100 --> 00:07:27,900
Isn't it obvious?

131
00:07:28,780 --> 00:07:29,800
I'll call you a tow truck

132
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,490
and take you to a repair shop.

133
00:07:33,270 --> 00:07:34,020
Let's go.

134
00:07:42,990 --> 00:07:43,510
Sir Xue.

135
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,220
We've got a customer!

136
00:07:47,190 --> 00:07:48,070
Little brat.

137
00:07:48,340 --> 00:07:49,750
Haven't seen you in a while.

138
00:07:51,280 --> 00:07:52,390
Let me take a look at you.

139
00:07:52,870 --> 00:07:54,100
I got into trouble recently.

140
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:54,790
Here I am.

141
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,390
As soon as I got out,
I came straight to you.

142
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:57,660
And I brought you a customer.

143
00:08:07,820 --> 00:08:13,260
